<i>adverb</i>: 자세히 [자세히], 자상히 [자상히], 세세히 [세ː세히] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>자세히 [자세히]</dt><br>
<dd>in detail; minutely</dd><br>
<dd>아주 사소한 부분까지 구체적이고 분명하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Concretely and clearly even in insignificant parts.</dd><br>
<dt>자상히 [자상히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. minutely; in detail</dd><br>
<dd>꼼꼼하고 자세하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a meticulous and detailed manner.</dd><br>
<dd>2. considerately; attentively; thoughtfully</dd><br>
<dd>인정이 많고 온갖 힘을 다하려는 마음이 깊게.</dd><br>
<dd>With compassion for others and a sincere mind to do all one can for them.</dd><br>
<dt>세세히 [세ː세히]</dt><br>
<dd>in detail; minutely</dd><br>
<dd>사소한 것까지 놓치거나 빠뜨리지 않고 아주 자세하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a great detail without missing or skipping a minor thing.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>